Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.65,0:03:37.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有事再開不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.94,0:03:42.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,議題什麼的無所謂  只是想開會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.82,0:03:43.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我想開會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:45.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,舉行職員會議吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:47.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,來開編輯會議了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.03,0:03:48.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:53.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,當作是為了交流去參加也是為人著想了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:55.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,交流很重要嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.54,0:04:01.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不過…會來擔心我的家庭會議什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.76,0:04:03.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,大家意外的都是好人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:07.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,會來擔心我的編輯會議什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:09.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,大家意外的都是好人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.72,0:04:12.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,會來擔心我的職員會議什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.02,0:04:14.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,大家意外的都是好人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:18.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不過說到底  果然還是想儘可能的不開會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:20.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:22.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,話說…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:25.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這個  是啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:27.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老井…吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.99,0:04:28.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,應該是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:31.37,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\pos(839.4,780.4)}是井邊會議
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:31.37,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,註：在日本江戶時代住在平房的主婦們經常能在取水洗衣的時候在水井處遇見，所以在井口旁聊起家常八卦的現象\N非常普遍，後被稱之為「井邊會議」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:33.87,kakushigoto in 2,,0,0,0,,{\frz333.1\pos(907.2,592)}最終回無動於衷的她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:33.87,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,註：標題源自高橋真的漫畫「最終兵器女友」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.33,0:04:35.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.62,0:04:36.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.33,0:04:37.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:41.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,會議室什麼時候能做好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.30,0:04:45.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,難道說真的有需要開會解決的議題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:49.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,能…能作為參考說說是什麼議題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:51.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是關於生日聚會的事情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:53.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,竟然是生日聚會？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.56,0:04:57.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不是  帶會議室的家很少見的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:04:59.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.44,0:05:01.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,至少咱家裡沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:05.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒有會議室也能開會的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.78,0:05:06.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那多不像樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:10.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我一直都以為會議得在會議室開才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:11.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在哪兒都行麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:12.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,水井
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:15.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是叫「井邊會議」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:17.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,找到水井的話就能開會了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:20.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,水井在東京還有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:22.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:27.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是要委託尋找水井  這麼理解可以麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:28.30,kakushigoto in 10 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\frz266.9\pos(817.6,555.2)}目黑川偵探事務所
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.68,0:05:32.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這個委託  就由目黑川偵探事務所接下了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:35.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我也是所員啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:38.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.02,0:05:41.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,竟然是關於生日聚會的會議
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.82,0:05:44.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬的生日  應該還有半年以上才對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.94,0:05:46.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好  確認了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.49,0:05:49.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這週也謝謝您了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:50.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:52.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我要進行料理的特訓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.91,0:05:57.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,變得能炸出怎麼吃都吃不完的美味炸雞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.37,0:06:01.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不相信那個時候我說的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:05.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,對了對了  多虧了您編輯會議平安結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.09,0:06:08.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,開過編輯會議了麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:11.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您不是還擔心過的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:13.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,為什麼我要擔心編輯會…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:15.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.97,0:06:15.72,kakushigoto in 5,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\c&H787776&\frz2.139\pos(462.4,147.2)}議題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.97,0:06:15.72,kakushigoto in 5,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\c&H777777&\frz1.441\pos(467.2,222.4)}連載陣容的更替
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.89,0:06:18.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這家店似乎很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:19.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但好像也挺貴呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:21.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:26.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,於是呢  主編問您下次要不要去吃好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.86,0:06:29.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,主編親自叫人出來…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.32,0:06:32.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是嗎  終於…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.66,0:06:33.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要腰斬了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:35.74,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}腰斬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.16,0:06:39.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真好啊  和主編一起去吃好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.21,0:06:41.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要去高檔的館子吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:42.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:46.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,主編專門請人去吃好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:48.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.17,0:06:50.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,做好覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:58.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,於是呢  後藤老師說下次去吃個飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.19,0:07:03.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,什麼情況  是什麼待遇上的不滿麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:06.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真討厭啊  和作者發生爭執什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:07.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那…那個麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:10.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,說起來好幾年都沒給安排彩頁了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.24,0:07:12.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那麼我就去訂店了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:29.42,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}大吃特吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:29.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真好吃啊  這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.71,0:07:31.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然是腰斬嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:34.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,具體是到多久呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.01,0:07:35.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}虎軀一震
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:38.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}果然是要求畫彩頁嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:40.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是…是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:42.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,儘可能快點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:45.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}再怎麼快也得四周以後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.81,0:07:46.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,儘可能快點？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:49.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}這麼突然故事結不了尾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.86,0:07:52.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這個是什麼做的啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.82,0:07:56.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,能十週之後就很感激了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.33,0:07:58.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這麼後面麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:08:00.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然太後面了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.37,0:08:04.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒有沒有  這種程度的話我也能準備了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.62,0:08:05.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,準備？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:06.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,關於什麼的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:07.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:09.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,彩頁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:13.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,彩頁…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:15.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:18.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.51,0:08:21.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,謝謝您的關懷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.73,0:08:27.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,太好了呢  不知為何拿到了彩頁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:30.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就跟分手費差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:37.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,用彩頁來完美收場  基本的人文關懷啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.32,0:08:37.62,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,700)\fs50\bord4\c&H32F5EE&\3c&H49495D&\frz21.27\move(280,697.6,281.2,587)}感動的最終回
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.32,0:08:37.62,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,700)\bord3\frz275\c&HC26E88&\move(502.4,838.4,503.2,711.6)}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.03,0:08:43.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,請旗下擔任的作家吃飯  還拿到了彩頁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.50,0:08:46.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我是個多麼優秀的責編啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:48.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這麼貴的館子的收據
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:51.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不是主編的話很難報銷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:08:56.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,該怎麼對大家說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.22,0:08:59.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是幫他們找好下家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.51,0:09:03.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,還是支付工資  等到下一部連載再開呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.39,0:09:07.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不  下一部連載要到何時
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.69,0:09:09.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在哪本雜誌上連載都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:14.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,收入也斷了  這樣的話錢再多都不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.78,0:09:21.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,連載的間隙對漫畫家來說可謂是逢魔之時
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:26.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不游下去就會死去的魚  要是放棄游動的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.67,0:09:29.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,想要再次游起來就不容易了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.59,0:09:33.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,恍惚之間一年過去了  兩年過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:36.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,被讀者和編輯們所忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.39,0:09:42.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,中斷的收入  持續下去的經費
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:44.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,眼看著儲蓄減少
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:46.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,卻看不見光明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.10,0:09:50.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,然後身心狀態變得不穩定的漫畫家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:53.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,會變得越來越想不出有趣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:55.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,陷入惡性循環
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:09:59.49,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fs75\frx34\fry352\frz33.79\move(873.6,249.6,72.8,249.4)}賬單
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:10:00.62,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\frx26\fry352\frz27.84\move(1502.4,307.2,314.6,310.4,0,3486)}需支付金額  210000日元
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:10:00.62,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\frx26\fry352\frz31.73\move(1556.8,723.2,380,712.8,0,3486)}租船費  1艘  80000日元
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:10:00.62,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\frx26\fry352\frz33.84\move(1624,926.4,465,906.6,0,3486)}潛水員費  2名  53000日元
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:10:00.62,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\frx26\fry352\frz33.84\move(1868.8,1049.6,687.4,1044.2,24,3486)}燃料費  1套  10000日元
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:09:59.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,即便不那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.07,0:10:02.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也要花錢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.51,0:10:19.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.68,0:10:23.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,被爐真是可怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:26.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,等爸爸的時候不知何時意識就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.18,0:10:28.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在被爐睡覺會感冒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:32.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,對了  我忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:35.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,歡迎回家  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.78,0:10:40.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我回來了  姬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.78,0:10:43.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,雖然不知道未來的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.37,0:10:46.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但作為父親在姬的面前還是以笑臉面對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:48.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:54.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,「風之緊身褲」還有十週就將完結了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.00,0:10:56.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.42,0:10:58.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真遺憾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:11:02.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你們也不吃驚一下  不傷感一下麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.64,0:11:05.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,為什麼要  總有一天會完結的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.64,0:11:07.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,稍微也失落一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:09.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你們不也會因為失去工作而困擾麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.31,0:11:13.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,差不多想要些時間畫自己作品了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.23,0:11:14.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:20.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我也差不多該好好去大學了  不拿到學分畢不了業
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:21.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:24.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我們的事情  請不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:27.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.24,0:11:29.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.54,0:11:31.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,顧慮我的心情而故意的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.21,0:11:32.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.33,0:11:36.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好  最後的衝刺了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.71,0:11:38.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一直畫到完結吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.51,0:11:43.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,現在我該做的  那便是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.64,0:11:45.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,集中於漫畫之上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.80,0:11:47.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,說是剛剛好…雖然有點那啥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:51.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,請讓我放假…有點難說出口呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.52,0:11:51.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:54.98,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\pos(275.2,256)}※\h\h意外的是這種理由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.73,0:12:01.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,居然親口發出了擬聲詞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:03.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這就是老師他全神貫注的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:05.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,嗯  看上去有些瘮人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.37,0:12:09.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,反正也要完了  那就想畫什麼就畫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.58,0:12:11.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,大幹一場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:18.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,喂  十丸院
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.67,0:12:22.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,最近的風之緊身褲突然變得有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.22,0:12:23.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:27.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然說了給他彩頁過後他就有幹勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:28.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.51,0:12:30.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,當腰斬定下來的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.06,0:12:33.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,像這樣漫畫突然變得有趣了的情況也時有發生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:39.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,太有趣了  但這梗也太狠了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:42.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師您這是全面開戰  完全不怕死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.32,0:12:45.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,哈哈  反正都要完結了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:49.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,無後顧之憂的漫畫家猶如受傷的狼一樣奮死一搏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:52.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這週的原稿也很有靈性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.41,0:12:54.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這下  緊身褲也就不用擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.91,0:12:56.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.58,0:13:00.25,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,畢竟有像我這麼優秀的責編
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:04.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,無後顧之憂的漫畫家通常會超常發揮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.05,0:13:08.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我打算去歐洲旅遊一週
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:09.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.01,0:13:12.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但前提是要能夠完結
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.81,0:13:16.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我們終於  發現了這口井
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:18.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,嗯  找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.73,0:13:21.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,現在開井邊會議還太冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.11,0:13:23.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,還沒什麼人使用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.07,0:13:26.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也就是會議隨便開囉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:28.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.45,0:13:31.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我得和爸爸開家庭會議了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.12,0:13:34.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:36.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我們可以開家庭會議了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.04,0:13:41.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,糟了  因為腰斬的事情完全搞忘了這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:43.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:47.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,因為最近忙工作  還沒來得及修建會議室
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.55,0:13:49.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒事的  我找到會場了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.39,0:13:51.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,會場？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:54.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,反正都是家裡的某處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.43,0:13:53.14,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\fs50\frz336\pos(500.8,380.8)\c&H727377&}會議中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:53.14,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\fs50\c&H626468&\pos(580.8,97.6)\frz356.5}比如這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.18,0:13:54.89,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\fs50\c&H727377&\pos(571.2,464)\frz24.08}會議中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.14,0:13:54.89,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\c&H626468&\frz356.5\pos(328,638.4)}比如這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.56,0:13:56.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但  確實…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.27,0:14:00.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,必須得開家庭會議了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.94,0:14:02.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,因為我快失業了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.44,0:14:04.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,即使沒了工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:08.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我也不會讓姬擔心和感到不安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.07,0:14:09.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,無論發生什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:12.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬期待著的生日聚會  我也要舉辦給你看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:14.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,失業了又怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.50,0:14:16.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.87,0:14:19.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,等明天下班後  我們來開家庭會議吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.34,0:14:27.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原稿我收下了  這週也同樣很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.42,0:14:28.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,應該吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:30.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那麼再見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:46.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,得趕緊回去了  不能讓姬擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:48.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.82,0:14:50.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,歡迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.03,0:14:51.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.49,0:14:52.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:56.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我先去準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.25,0:14:58.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我們走吧  洛克
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:05.29,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\c&H6C55C2&\3c&HF6DBFB&\b1\move(516,330,506,254,0,1818)\frz10.84}家庭會議  指引圖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:05.29,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\c&H6C55C2&\3c&HE3E3E3&\b1\frz22.4\move(134,510,24,456,0,1818)}小學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:05.29,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\c&H6C55C2&\3c&HF6DBFB&\frz10.05\b1\move(750,802,660,732,0,1818)}河
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:05.29,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\c&H6C55C2&\3c&HFDFDE1&\frz12.3\b1\move(1448,646,1358,572,0,1818)}會場
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:05.29,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\c&H6C55C2&\3c&HF9FFD8&\frz10.05\b1\move(1462,966,1380,890,0,1818)}井
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:05.29,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\c&H6C55C2&\3c&H72E290&\b1\frz14.37\move(1616,922,1530,848,0,1818)}公園
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,0:15:04.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,井
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.59,0:15:07.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原來是井邊會議啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.21,0:15:09.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這樣確實能夠開會了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:15.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要掉下去了怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.06,0:15:19.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是姬的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.23,0:15:21.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬  你掉下去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.11,0:15:26.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒…掉下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.48,0:15:27.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那為什麼你要大叫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.78,0:15:29.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,裡邊兒有聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:30.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,聲音？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:34.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,1張  2張
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.53,0:15:38.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}3張…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:40.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這裡不是番町皿屋敷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:43.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您搞錯地方出沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:43.17,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,註：番町皿屋敷是指夜晚亡靈在井裡數碟子的日本傳統鬼故事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:43.17,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,日語中張和枚發音相同
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:48.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,4張  5張
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.63,0:15:50.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,快逃  姬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:53.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}6張  7張
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.42,0:15:51.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是  爸爸你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.47,0:15:53.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,洛克  快走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.39,0:15:56.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.01,0:15:56.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}8張…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.64,0:15:58.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,9張…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.06,0:16:02.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,10…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.23,0:16:05.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,張
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.19,0:16:09.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師  我找回了10張
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.49,0:16:17.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原稿是16張
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.49,0:16:20.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我交給你的是複印稿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.41,0:16:23.25,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能給十丸院先生手稿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.54,0:16:24.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,能幹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.16,0:16:23.21,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\fs65\bord3\frz270\c&HDCB9BB&\3c&H000000&\pos(1594,462)}能幹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.21,0:16:23.25,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\fs65\bord3\frz270\c&HDCB9BB&\3c&H000000&\pos(1292,460)}能幹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.25,0:16:23.29,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\fs65\bord3\frz270\c&HDCB9BB&\3c&H000000&\pos(1152,466)}能幹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.29,0:16:23.33,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\fs65\bord3\frz270\c&HDCB9BB&\3c&H000000&\pos(1100,466)}能幹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.33,0:16:24.58,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\fs65\bord3\frz270\c&HDCB9BB&\3c&H000000&\pos(1086,464)}能幹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.17,0:16:27.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就先不說了  讓他好好反省一陣子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.46,0:16:29.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,哭唧唧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.25,0:16:33.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,說起來  還不是老師您沒有用電子畫板我才成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.26,0:16:35.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那個我不用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.51,0:16:38.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我感覺還是傳統的更有靈魂一些
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.81,0:16:41.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,離最終回也不遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.10,0:16:45.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,最終回？您指的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.40,0:16:50.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我也打算去遠處逛兩週
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.07,0:16:53.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我也訂好了取材旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.20,0:16:55.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,接下來有好多有趣的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:16:57.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,大伙兒  高興吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.16,0:17:01.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,緊身褲不會完結了  要繼續連載
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.04,0:17:07.04,kakushigoto in 5,,0,0,0,,{\c&H7C685E&\pos(1038,412)}風之緊身褲\N{\fs60}\h讀者調查問卷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.50,0:17:09.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,結果只是一瞬間的高光時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.13,0:17:12.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就算責編再怎麼優秀  也是有極限的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:15.55,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\pos(864,340)}會議中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.88,0:17:18.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你說的生日聚會  是你朋友的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:19.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.31,0:17:22.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.27,0:17:26.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以  關於生日聚會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.35,0:17:29.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我去向她表明拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.86,0:17:32.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是  如果我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.19,0:17:35.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就得招待她們來我的生日聚會了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.53,0:17:37.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我們家不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:41.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,只有爸爸你一個人準備太辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:43.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,難道  又是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:45.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,炸雞塊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.29,0:17:47.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,炸雞塊?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.46,0:17:48.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.63,0:17:54.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,因為大家定好了  要帶自己做的菜去參加生日聚會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.63,0:17:58.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以我覺得生日聚會一定少不了炸雞塊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.22,0:18:03.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是  我還不能一個人炸東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.56,0:18:08.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以我想  能不能讓爸爸你幫幫我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:17.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊  原來是炸雞塊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.61,0:18:18.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.36,0:18:21.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我們一起炸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:26.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸也得為了準備你的生日聚會  還得不斷練習
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.00,0:18:27.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,謝謝爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.54,0:18:30.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那麼我們現在就來練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.88,0:18:34.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,當然好  我沒有任何理由反駁你的意見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.01,0:18:38.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  家庭會議真不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:43.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是啊  下次就有關姬的生日聚會來開會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.35,0:18:46.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,誒  還有半年以上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.94,0:18:56.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.53,0:19:05.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,祝你生日快樂  姬小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.12,0:19:12.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:14.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.72,0:19:20.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.76,0:19:21.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:22.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.22,0:19:23.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,請收下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.05,0:19:27.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我就是世界第一可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.27,0:19:32.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,小姬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.02,0:19:36.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.87,0:19:51.37,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}11歲生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.12,0:19:53.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,再次恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.92,0:19:57.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,生日快樂  姬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.46,0:20:00.51,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我11歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.67,0:20:03.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這是給你的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:05.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我可以打開嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.56,0:20:09.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是八音盒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:10.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你很想要的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.06,0:20:11.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.77,0:20:14.52,kakushigoto in 2,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\c&H282932&\pos(712,220.666)\frz359.1}送給姬的11歲生日禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.77,0:20:14.52,kakushigoto in 2,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\c&H282932&\pos(812.667,332)}生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.27,0:20:16.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.77,0:20:21.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你真的為我辦了兩次生日聚會了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.74,0:20:23.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,因為我答應過你了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.70,0:20:25.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,和朋友們的生日聚會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.24,0:20:28.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,還有和爸爸單獨的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.95,0:20:31.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是三人的生日聚會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.46,0:20:35.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,以後每年我們都這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.13,0:20:42.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  今後也請多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.09,0:20:45.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我才是  今後也請你多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.18,0:20:51.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我以為這樣的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.18,0:20:52.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,會一直
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.43,0:20:54.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一直
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.35,0:20:56.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,持續下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.12,0:21:19.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  今天我就18歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.10,0:21:37.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,鑰匙還有地圖？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.24,0:21:48.24,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}隱瞞之事  有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.75,0:22:00.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,隱瞞之事究竟是什麼
